@node Main "Bloksters - Documentation"

                            'Bloksters' 1.01

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" Bloksters " link play} is a Workbench game where the goal is simple: send
blocks inside the game arena so that they make line-ups of 4 blocks
or more of the same colour, either horizontally or vertically. When
at least 4 blocks of the same colour are lined-up, they are then
eliminated from the board and you get points according to the
number of removed blocks.

  The catch is that, whenever a block is sent and does not complete
a line-up of at least 4 blocks of the same colour, a new block will
randomly appear in the arena... which you can guess, may complicate
matters a little. Also, a block must be in line, horizontally or
vertically, with the block you want to send.

  Have fun!

